The paper deals with automated image enhancement using machine learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Gaussian process for parameter search and ranking also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of subjective tests, which could indicate a connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in terms of evaluating the effectiveness of the proposed approach.
